{"tid":316391,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手想養蛙求指教","createTime":"2017-07-10T16:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T09:50:54.000Z","uid":12512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a96e659be7177b5283814a1d66a08282515df46d","tid":316391,"uid":12512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:30:22.000Z","msg":"已經上網做過好多research 但可能冷門所以唔太多資料 求養開既巴打指教<br />\n<br />\n1. 想問下邊度買？<br />\n上網睇好多都話街舖唔好 見到有推介綠之園or魚佬<br />\n<br />\n2. 暫時對角蛙/牛蛙/樹蛙有興趣 想問下佢地各有咩特性同養佢地有咩要注意？ 已知角蛙好似攻擊性大啲<br />\n<br />\n3. 設備同糧食洗費一個月大概幾多？<br />\n<br />\n跪求連登養蛙巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0552879e36ebf91df84498f2d234b411f0b111d0","tid":316391,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ede4266f104d57f8b52a465e50af490e7028805c","tid":316391,"uid":12512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溫水煮</blockquote><br />\n從前有三隻蝦......<br />\n不過都多謝你幫我推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a6b199b567b838666446c749661597147177f1","tid":316391,"uid":12512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e045c7d5fa4b07fca6488a66c11adfad7a5607","tid":316391,"uid":12512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T00:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb8c4aeae1812774e545d6e74c3f3888d7b2cc9","tid":316391,"uid":17162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:50:54.000Z","msg":"魚街周圍都有得買 普普通通 150蚊都有一隻， 上fb d 交流群組都有好多人賣，<br />\n缸睇你鐘意啦 有貴有平 我就用好平既飼養盒30幾蚊。<br />\n食物 我買一包35蚊 浸水果d糧 好似食左兩個月先用完一包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （可能我餵得少）"}]}